examples.en: He was beaten and robbed by street thugs.
He was beaten up by a gang of young thugs.
A few thugs terrorized the city with beating, stabbing, and shooting.
Before I knew what was happening, the thug had run through me with a knife.
Beneath his suave, polished exterior lay the truculence of a common street thug.
The Mob boss regularly sent his thugs after people who were slow to pay their debts.
